{
  "texts": [
    "The classic methods cannot accurately estimate the critical time, so a three-dimensional warning gating network is used, giving greater importance to rising moments.",
    "Thus, deep-reinforcement learning tools obtain more substantial returns and improve profit indicators while reducing risk (Weng et al., 2020).",
    "In other research, recurrent consolidation learning has successfully optimized portfolios.",
    "It memorizes up-to-date market conditions and constantly rebalances the portfolio's content based on classic performance indicators (Aboussalah and Lee, 2020).",
    "In some models, a compromise parameter is introduced to adjust the portfolio's optimism level, and learning algorithms evaluate market fluctuations and provide information to generate forecast hyperparameters."
  ]
}